flavor_text: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig upfood. It sometimes discovers hot springs.
If it smells some thing enticing it dashes headlongoff to find the source of the aroma.
It uses the tip of its nose to dig for food. Its noseis so tough that even frozen ground poses no problem.
SWINUB roots for food by rubbing its snout against the ground. Its favorite food is a mushroom that grows underthe cover of dead grass. This Pokemon occasionally roots out hot springs.
